# Eval result JSONs contain real record IDs and query text from
# the user's data — same privacy posture as the labelled golden
# YAML. Keep them out of the repo by default.
#
# To track a baseline reference deliberately, force-add with:
#   git add -f evals/retrieval/results/baseline.json
# but first scrub IDs by hand.

*.json
!.gitkeep
